f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70265176606e5b9334ae2f9d9f2c436d5d593ab","tid":215264,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我條魚有呢個問題已經三個幾月咩都冇搞過<br />\n每日都睇佢係到旋轉/反肚<br />\n都幾治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bab09f15d232b5fad350ee8ae17a0b2cdffdb0","tid":215264,"uid":36080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"我估可能係水問題"},{"pid":"d5469152d154828dff3d029dbbc9b22ff228886f","tid":215264,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我估可能係水問題</blockquote><br />\n不如樓主貼下相出來啦睇睇？<br />\n咩資料都無大家都係估估下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bb47099b5ee17b5a3c4209971e82c396033978","tid":215264,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T00:27:26.000Z","msg":"試過唔喂野比佢食<br />\n反反下冇反"},{"pid":"cac546ed06cff9dccdef93cac9798ff92124bc4a","tid":215264,"uid":36080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuCE8J1.jpg&h=65f97f48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25P7963.jpg&h=faf52a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知個缸唔夠大<br />\n得閒會換個大缸比佢"},{"pid":"53f8c2643daf5b28f28316c5eacc6355381bec60","tid":215264,"uid":71389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuCE8J1.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4f216938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg[img]</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25P7963.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f11285ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg[img]</a><br />\n我知個缸唔夠大<br />\n得閒會換個大缸比佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 金魚絕對不可以養在小缸、圓缸<br />\n<br />\n　金魚隨著飼主的餵食　他的器官不停的生長　<br />\n　如果缸子太小　金魚會緊迫　造成體型不長、器官一直在長<br />\n　浮標受到脂肪和其他器官嚴重擠壓　導致浮標失調　也會大幅縮短金魚壽命<br />\n　許多歐洲國家禁止販售小缸圓缸　<br />\n　因為器官受到擠壓的金魚　在死之前要忍受一段極度痛苦而且漫長的過程<br />\n　這是嚴重虐待動物的行為 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20091204000010KK00171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20091204000010KK00171&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1595466f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20091204000010KK00171</a>"},{"pid":"366ac0f338b6f9d3b87d232d58ba1596d8cd0f99","tid":215264,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuCE8J1.jpg&h=65f97f48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25P7963.jpg&h=faf52a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知個缸唔夠大<br />\n得閒會換個大缸比佢</blockquote><br />\n蘭壽最容易有魚漂病"},{"pid":"924b1f07feaed023f692bde59995a211001a6036","tid":215264,"uid":36080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ffe5120d69821077edc45fc4d2e5235878c8e1","tid":215264,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[img][url]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg[img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuCE8J1.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9dadbf5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg[img][/url]</a><br />\n[img][url]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg[img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25P7963.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1f249c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg[img][/url]</a><br />\n我知個缸唔夠大<br />\n得閒會換個大缸比佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 金魚絕對不可以養在小缸、圓缸<br />\n<br />\n　金魚隨著飼主的餵食　他的器官不停的生長　<br />\n　如果缸子太小　金魚會緊迫　造成體型不長、器官一直在長<br />\n　浮標受到脂肪和其他器官嚴重擠壓　導致浮標失調　也會大幅縮短金魚壽命<br />\n　許多歐洲國家禁止販售小缸圓缸　<br />\n　因為器官受到擠壓的金魚　在死之前要忍受一段極度痛苦而且漫長的過程<br />\n　這是嚴重虐待動物的行為 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20091204000010KK00171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20091204000010KK00171&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1595466f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20091204000010KK00171</a></blockquote><br />\n圓缸禁售原因係令金魚視覺折磨<br />\n<a href=\"http://mobile.abc.net.au/news/2004-07-24/council-bans-goldfish-bowls/2014352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmobile.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2004-07-24%2Fcouncil-bans-goldfish-bowls%2F2014352&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=144784f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://mobile.abc.net.au/news/2004-07-24/council-bans-goldfish-bowls/2014352</a><br />\n細缸我無聽過禁售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇詳細新聞睇下？"},{"pid":"cd53fa529f23c88b7b1bf1606b95d14ad9fc78c4","tid":215264,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuCE8J1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuCE8J1.jpg&h=65f97f48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25P7963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25P7963.jpg&h=faf52a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知個缸唔夠大<br />\n得閒會換個大缸比佢</blockquote><br />\n蘭壽最容易有魚漂病</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而有啲金魚會有先天性問題<br />\n有啲就食飽先會失平衡<br />\n有啲就唔會<br />\n<br />\n如果係呢啲情況<br />\n唔係因為咩病嘅話<br />\n唯有禁食幾日，平時餵少啲<br />\n餵嘅糧買返啲正常金魚糧<br />\n例如Hikari牌櫻花綠色袋裝<br />\n樓上舖賞魚閣買最平（好似係）<br />\n另外聽講餵烚青豆可以改善腸胃<br />\n記住搣走層皮先餵<br />\n間中餵下調理下唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}